      <title>创建了一个「狂人日记」</title>
      <link>https://elizen.me/posts/2020/04/%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BA%E4%BA%86%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E7%8B%82%E4%BA%BA%E6%97%A5%E8%AE%B0/</link>
